<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA76">
<l>uḷḷilu muḷḷan taṭikkum viṉaippaṭalam</l>
<l>viḷḷa viḻittuṉṉai meyyuṟṟā luḷḷa</l>
<l>vulakaḷavu yāṉu muḷaṉāva ṉeṉko</l>
<l>lulakaḷanta mūrtti yurai.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When I think of [you my] mind enlarges and when I open my eyes</l>
<l>[and] truly behold you, so that the masses of Karma crack, I too</l>
<l>will be one who is of the measure of the world. What [is this],</l>
<l>o form that measured they world, tell [me].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
